  <brief_title>The Effect of Sitagliptin in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus With Inadequate Glycemic Control (MK0431-118)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-label, Non Placebo-Controlled Study To Verify the Effect of Sitagliptin In Adult Patients With Type 2 Diabetes and Inadequate Glycemic Control</official_title>
